      "description": "Karan, the illegitimate son cast aside by the powerful Abhiraj Irani, returns determined to bring his father to his knees. Using cunning and unrelenting ambition, he outsmarts Abhiraj’s loyal heir, Arjun, and draws Devika into his web of vengeance. But as Karan dismantles the empire that denied him, he grapples with the burden of betrayal, the pull of forbidden love, and the question of whether he is becoming the very man he despises.",
